China's top advisory body, has performed good services for the
country's reform, opening-up and modernization drive and
contributed greatly to China's peaceful reunification.
</P>
<P>
This view was shared by the 2,195 members of the Ninth CPPCC
National Committee, which opened its first annual session Tuesday,
during their panels today on a work report by the Standing
Committee of the previous CPPCC National Committee.
</P>
<P>
The members agreed that China's current good situation has
created favorable conditions for the smooth development of various
kinds of work of the Eighth CPPCC National Committee, and that the
correct leadership of the Communist Party of China (CPC) Central
Committee has provided a basic guarantee for the constant progress
of the work of the CPPCC.
</P>
<P>
They pointed out that it was under the guidance of Deng
Xiaoping Theory that the Eighth CPPCC National Committee has
scored tremendous achievements, and that Deng Xiaoping should be
regarded as founder of the CPPCC work in the new period of reform
and opening-up.
</P>
<P>
They also attributed the successes of the Eighth CPPCC National
Committee to the work of the CPC Central Committee with Jiang
Zemin at the core, which has always attached great importance to
the CPPCC.
</P>
<P>
