railways, 551 km of double-track railways, new harbors or enlarged
ones with a combined cargo handling capacity of 117.25 million
tons, 19.61 million lines of the installed capacity of urban
telephone switchboards, 27,000 km of long-distance fiber-optical
cables, 14,000 km of newly constructed microwave digital
telecommunication lines, and 1,313 km of newly constructed
expressways.  
