1997, the State Statistics Bureau announced here today.
</P>
<P>
In the year, 188 companies issued 10.6 billion A shares at
Shanghai and Shenzhen stock exchanges, with capital paid-in
topping 65.5 billion yuan. The total number of listed companies in
the two stock market increased to 745 from 530.
</P>
