<HEADLINE> Italian President Hails China's Reform </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ROME, March 3 (Xinhua) -- Italian President Oscar Luigi
Scalfaro said his country is closely observing the social and
economic progress China has made over the past few years.
</P>
