<TEXT>
<P>
BRASILIA, March 3 (Xinhua) -- Brazil's export of beef amounted
to 275,000 tons in 1997, an increase of 4 percent over 1996, the
Brazilian Association of Meat Exporting Industries said Tuesday.
</P>
